26/10/2012: Kees Jan de Vries

For this functionality to work, you need to install HepMC
go to icgapp.cern.ch/project/simu/HepMC/download/
Click on "source" on the right.

Go into the directory "HepMC-*.*.*" and do "make"
Then go into the "test" directory and do "make"

Upon running compile.sh, the file testHepMC.cc will be copied to the
HepMC-*.*.*/test/ directory, and then compiled
please SPECIFY this directory compile.sh

